                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18141026-67-defend669 t18141026-67-punish387"></join>
               DEATH
            </rs>, aged 20.</p>
               <p>First Middlesex Jury, before Mr. Baron Riehards.</p>
